sec.p:
The longer memory sequence w is kept if and only if the information gain is greater than some threshold K [5, 6]. Refer to Section 3.3 for a discussion on the value of K. The set of all sequences that respect the above threshold are called contexts, and denoted by T:


T={w∈WD|ΔHw>K}

(S10)

A VLMC is the the Markov model with the set of states:


L={wx|  t∈T,x∈χ}

(S11)
